  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Establish Rome’s frontier in untamed barbarian territory. Build a legionary camp, command your soldiers, and carve a Roman stronghold out of the wilderness.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a Roman legionary sent to the edge of the Empire. In the wild north of Hispania, far from the safety of Rome, your mission is simple: establish a foothold, secure the territory, and survive whatever the frontier throws at you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056200/extras/572e2b76ca6dd8a46911e9e08c25ceae.poster.avif?t=1773335148\" width=1170 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056200/extras/572e2b76ca6dd8a46911e9e08c25ceae.webm?t=1773335148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056200/extras/572e2b76ca6dd8a46911e9e08c25ceae.mp4?t=1773335148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start with a small expedition camp and transform it into a thriving Roman stronghold. Gather resources, construct fortifications, recruit and manage your soldiers, and lead your people through a harsh and unpredictable land. As your influence grows, so will your responsibilities... and your path from common legionary to respected centurion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056200/extras/a7ddb517fa5dc96b428b4b1849702bb0.poster.avif?t=1773335148\" width=1170 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056200/extras/a7ddb517fa5dc96b428b4b1849702bb0.webm?t=1773335148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056200/extras/a7ddb517fa5dc96b428b4b1849702bb0.mp4?t=1773335148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BUILD A ROMAN CAMP</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Construct barracks, workshops, and defenses to turn a small expedition into a thriving frontier camp.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COMMAND YOUR LEGIONARIES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assign soldiers to gather resources, craft equipment, and defend your settlement.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SURVIVE THE FRONTIER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face hostile tribes, harsh conditions, and the dangers of unexplored lands.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RISE THROUGH THE RANKS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow from a lone legionary into a respected commander of Rome’s expedition.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Summa Expeditionis is more than a game: <strong>it’s a test of wit, courage, and leadership</strong>. Will you answer Rome’s call?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💥 <strong>Play now in Early Access and help shape the ultimate Roman Empire experience!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056200/extras/eab21620cc9902e0a3a69490cfe280b6.poster.avif?t=1773335148\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056200/extras/eab21620cc9902e0a3a69490cfe280b6.webm?t=1773335148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056200/extras/eab21620cc9902e0a3a69490cfe280b6.mp4?t=1773335148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Establish Rome’s frontier in untamed barbarian territory. Build a legionary camp, command your soldiers, and carve a Roman stronghold out of the wilderness.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a Roman legionary sent to the edge of the Empire. In the wild north of Hispania, far from the safety of Rome, your mission is simple: establish a foothold, secure the territory, and survive whatever the frontier throws at you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056200/extras/572e2b76ca6dd8a46911e9e08c25ceae.poster.avif?t=1773335148\" width=1170 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056200/extras/572e2b76ca6dd8a46911e9e08c25ceae.webm?t=1773335148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056200/extras/572e2b76ca6dd8a46911e9e08c25ceae.mp4?t=1773335148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start with a small expedition camp and transform it into a thriving Roman stronghold. Gather resources, construct fortifications, recruit and manage your soldiers, and lead your people through a harsh and unpredictable land. As your influence grows, so will your responsibilities... and your path from common legionary to respected centurion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056200/extras/a7ddb517fa5dc96b428b4b1849702bb0.poster.avif?t=1773335148\" width=1170 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056200/extras/a7ddb517fa5dc96b428b4b1849702bb0.webm?t=1773335148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056200/extras/a7ddb517fa5dc96b428b4b1849702bb0.mp4?t=1773335148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BUILD A ROMAN CAMP</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Construct barracks, workshops, and defenses to turn a small expedition into a thriving frontier camp.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COMMAND YOUR LEGIONARIES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assign soldiers to gather resources, craft equipment, and defend your settlement.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SURVIVE THE FRONTIER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face hostile tribes, harsh conditions, and the dangers of unexplored lands.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RISE THROUGH THE RANKS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow from a lone legionary into a respected commander of Rome’s expedition.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Summa Expeditionis is more than a game: <strong>it’s a test of wit, courage, and leadership</strong>. Will you answer Rome’s call?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💥 <strong>Play now in Early Access and help shape the ultimate Roman Empire experience!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056200/extras/eab21620cc9902e0a3a69490cfe280b6.poster.avif?t=1773335148\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056200/extras/eab21620cc9902e0a3a69490cfe280b6.webm?t=1773335148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056200/extras/eab21620cc9902e0a3a69490cfe280b6.mp4?t=1773335148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
